In this section we discuss the additional clues that come from the stellar populations. The (very small, or even absent) star-to-star spread in [Fe/H] and α\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
