				\begin{document}$\varSigma _{\mathrm{SFR}}$\end{document} relations as showed here for observations in Fig. 10. They suggest that not only gas surface density and pressure (via the dependence from ΣSFR\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
